org.apache.struts2.portlet
Class PortletSessionMap

java.lang.Object

      org.apache.struts2.portlet.PortletSessionMap
All Implemented Interfaces:
Map<String,Object>
public class PortletSessionMap
extends AbstractMap<String,Object>

A simple implementation of the Map interface to handle a collection of portlet session attributes. The entrySet() method enumerates over all session attributes and creates a Set of entries. Note, this will occur lazily - only when the entry set is asked for.
